有一个名为 Grade_prd 的节点，其作用是：Student Grade System。

该节点接受输入：input: Any - System input，产生输出：output: Any - System output。

为了实现这个节点，我们计划将其分解为以下 10 个子节点：

- ParseCommand：Parse the input to extract command and grade_data.。签名：def ParseCommand(input: Any) -> Tuple[str, dict]
- RouteCommand：Route the command to the appropriate handler.。签名：def RouteCommand(command: str, grade_data: dict) -> dict
- HandleRecordGrade：Record a grade for a student in a course.。签名：def HandleRecordGrade(grade_data: dict) -> dict
- HandleUpdateGrade：Update an existing grade record.。签名：def HandleUpdateGrade(grade_data: dict) -> dict
- HandleDeleteGrade：Delete a grade record.。签名：def HandleDeleteGrade(grade_data: dict) -> dict
- HandleGetStudentGrades：Retrieve all grades for a student with computed average, total credits, GPA.。签名：def HandleGetStudentGrades(grade_data: dict) -> dict
- HandleGetCourseGrades：Retrieve all grades for a course with computed statistics.。签名：def HandleGetCourseGrades(grade_data: dict) -> dict
- HandleListClassGrades：List grades for students in a specific class, optionally filtered by course.。签名：def HandleListClassGrades(grade_data: dict) -> dict
- HandleGetGradeReport：Generate a textual grade report for a student.。签名：def HandleGetGradeReport(grade_data: dict) -> dict
- HandleGetCourseStats：Compute statistics for a course: average, standard deviation, pass rate, grade distribution percentages.。签名：def HandleGetCourseStats(grade_data: dict) -> dict

